715669f-a.title: Manhattan: 151st Street (West) - Macombs Place
715669f-a.text:
West 15lut Street, east from Macombs Place (foreground), showing
on the north side of the street a portion of the new slum clearance
development constructed by the Federal Government under the P.W.A.
housing program.
March 6, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
